name: Welcome Message
subject: Welcome to main@lists.tungsten.io
message:
Hello,

Welcome to the main@lists.tungsten.io group at Tungsten Fabric. Please take a moment to review this message.

To learn more about the main@lists.tungsten.io group, please visit https://lists.tungsten.io/g/main

To start sending messages to members of this group, simply send email to main@lists.tungsten.io

If you do not wish to belong to main@lists.tungsten.io, you may unsubscribe by sending an email to main+unsubscribe@lists.tungsten.io

To see and modify all of your groups, go to https://lists.tungsten.io


Regards,

The main@lists.tungsten.io Moderator
You have been added to the announce@ mailing list because it is a requirement to be a member of sub mailing lists such as tf-tsc-private@lists.tungsten.io
